rms - For god’s sake ask contact number. </b>\r\n\r\nIt is very easy to enter phone number.  Sometimes, easier than typing your own name.\r\n\r\nEnquiry forms should be easily accessible. These forms should have least number of mandatory fields.  The information that you would like to have, but not required can move to a second non-mandatory form.  If you know how to contact your customer, it is easier to call him up and get the remaining information.', '5 Web Design Tips For Internet Marketers - How to Sell More with Less Traffic', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '71-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-31 09:58:54', '2016-05-31 09:58:54', '', 71, 'https://intuisyz.com/blog/2016/05/31/71-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
